                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> <blockquote id="quote"><font size="2" face="Verdana" id="quote">quote:<hr height="1" noshade id="quote"><i>Originally posted by Krule Intentions</i><br /><br />So you cast fear and he just runs into the wall? Sounds like an exploit and being a Necro, it will get you banned. If you get caught.<br /><br />I try and avoid these. Sure I level up fast, but my skills get rusty, and then I suck some for a while after. On Tribunal the GM's (when on) have been cracking down hard on all PoP exploits, like the fear wall in PoJ. This sounds very similar.<br /><br />One guildie got a warning, one Banned. He is working on gettng cleared, but well you know.<br /><br />Not criticizing. Just be very careful. All it takes is one ass to report you because they are jealouse of you hunting in this manner.<br /><br />Krule Intentions<br />62 Warlock<br /><hr height="1" noshade id="quote"></blockquote id="quote"></font id="quote">I dunno if you are referring to this guide or not, but the above mentioned spot in PoD DOES have a little exploit that can be easily avoided.  If you fear a goo NEAR the corner of the bone wall, the goo will path back and forth, and slowly creep up the wall.  Not a MAJOR exploit like the PoJ hall, but an exploit none the less. <br /><br />To avoid this I simply moved a bit closer to the Court yard entrance, then when I feared the mob would NOT path back and forth, it would move down the hill i was on, and up another hill, fear would wear off, mob would path back to me, I'd refear and it would again path away.  It is MUCH easier to hunt here using THAT method, than to exploit and fear in the corner.  Safer, easier, unbannable method.<br /><br />Plus it could be argued that the minor corner pathing exploit (bone wall corner) ISN'T and exploit at all, since it sorta does move up the wall slowly, but VERY slowly...<br /><br />If SOE should fix ANY exploit in PoD it should be the castle wall, now THAT is a MAJOR FOOKING EXPLOIT, and it is a SAD day when I see people using it...especially necro's since it is SOOO easy to just aggro-kite/root-dot there.<br /><br /><b>Deedrok - Level 63<br />Warlock of E'ci<br />  <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234678" target="_blank"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234678" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234678</a></a></b></span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
